summary: Marvel Zombies RP Wanted Connection: Carol Danvers Requested by: Jessica Drew Telephone networks have failed, the internet is...
caption:
Marvel Zombies RP Wanted Connection: Carol Danvers
Requested by: Jessica Drew

Telephone networks have failed, the internet is gone. Modern communication seems to have come to an end. What remains is radiowaves. People with the right equipment have begun to communicate with anyone in range using CB radios, walkie talkies, whatever they can get their hands on. Some are broadcasting, some are just listening.

Carol slowly tuned through the channels on the old radio, she had crash landed on her reentry into the Earth’s atmosphere, and when she made it to Manhattan, the Tower was a wreckage. She heard the crackling sound of numbers coming through as she found an active channel –

This is Jessica Drew broadcasting for Carol Danvers. On the off chance you’re not in space and you’re out there, there’s somewhere safe. Haven. I’m here with Gerry. Clint is here. And Peter. Nat, Bobbi, Tony… I’ve saved you a room so you better get your ass here before someone steals it. Hope to see you soon! Love you, Kirk. Co-ordinates to follow…

Marvel Zombies RP is a Marvel Comics AU roleplay established 1 April 2017. We look forward to surviving with you.

summary:
It kills me when my dad 'jokingly' mocks female superheroes. 
Me: *after watching Scott Pilgrim with my dad* Ya know that chick...
body:
It kills me when my dad ‘jokingly’ mocks female superheroes.

Me: *after watching Scott Pilgrim with my dad* Ya know that chick who has, or had the vegan boyfriend?

Dad: Ex-Vegan.

Me: Right? Anyways, her actress is Brie Larson. She’s gonna be Captain Marvel.

Dad: She can’t be Captain Marvel. Captain Marvel is a man.

Me: In the DC universe, yes. But not in Marvel.

Dad: ????

Me: Different universes dad. Not the same person. Same name. Different hero. Marvel’s Captain Marvel, or Carol Danvers, was in the Airforce and she got these powers from this kree guy, look I don’t know all the details but she’s like a total badass. She’s got a movie coming out soon.

Dad: Female version. Right.

Me: No. Different people. DIFFERENT Universes. DC’s Captain Marvel is a 10 year old kid. Marvel’s Captain Marvel is a woman, a bad ass woman, she was in the Airforce.

Dad: Great. What’s next the Hulk with boobs?

Me: You must be thinking of She-Hulk. I think her name is Jennifer Walters? She’s Bruce Banner’s cousin, and she’s a lawyer-

Dad: *rolls his eyes and leaves the room*

Me: *growing irritated*

Dad: Let me guess, there’s a She-Thor?

Me: No, dad. It’s just Thor. But, people have referred to her as Lady Thor to make things less confusing. She’s actually Jane Foster, you see Thor became unworthy or he found himself unworthy something like that, and then he gave up the hammer. Jane got ahold of it and gained the-

Dad: So what is there now a Ms. Coulson too? A Katie Coulson? *scoffs*

Me: *trying to hold back my irritation* Women need superheros to look up to too..
